---
STATIC MOCKS  (defined in mocks/example.yaml)
---

1. Health Check

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/health

// Response 200
{ "status": "ok" }

---
2. Slow Endpoint (1.5s delay)

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/slow

// Response 200  (after 1500ms)
{ "message": "This response was intentionally delayed" }

---
3. Server Error

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/error

// Response 500
{ "error": "Internal Server Error", "message": "Something went wrong" }

---
4. Unauthorized

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/unauthorized

// Response 401
{ "error": "Unauthorized", "message": "Missing or invalid token" }

---
5. Custom Headers

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/custom-headers

// Response 200
// Response Headers: X-Custom-Header: my-value, X-Request-Id: abc-123
{ "message": "Response includes custom headers" }


