---
DYNAMIC ENDPOINTS  (built-in routes with runtime behaviour)
---

16. Echo

// Request
POST http://localhost:8000/echo
{ "name": "Alice", "role": "admin" }

// Response 200
{
  "name": "Alice",
  "role": "admin",
  "timestamp": "2026-04-13T10:30:00.000000+00:00"
}

---
17. Authenticated Echo — Valid Token

// Request
POST http://localhost:8000/echo/secure
Authorization: Bearer a3f1c2d4-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
{ "name": "Alice", "role": "admin" }

// Response 200
{
  "name": "Alice",
  "role": "admin",
  "timestamp": "2026-04-13T10:30:00.000000+00:00"
}

---
18. Authenticated Echo — Missing Token

// Request
POST http://localhost:8000/echo/secure
{ "name": "Alice" }

// Response 401
{ "valid": false, "error": "Missing or malformed Authorization header. Expected: Bearer <token>" }

---
19. Authenticated Echo — Invalid/Expired Token

// Request
POST http://localhost:8000/echo/secure
Authorization: Bearer invalid-or-expired-token
{ "name": "Alice" }

// Response 401
{ "valid": false, "error": "Token is invalid or expired" }

---
20. Get Token

// Request
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/token

// Response 201
{
  "token": "a3f1c2d4-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx",
  "expires_at": "2026-04-13T11:00:00.000000+00:00",
  "expires_in": 1800
}

---
21. Validate Token — Valid

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer a3f1c2d4-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

// Response 200
{ "valid": true, "message": "Token is valid" }

---
22. Validate Token — Invalid or Expired

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer invalid-or-expired-token

// Response 401
{ "valid": false, "error": "Token is invalid or expired" }

---
23. Validate Token — Missing Header

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/auth/validate

// Response 401
{ "valid": false, "error": "Missing or malformed Authorization header. Expected: Bearer <token>" }


---
ADMIN API  (mock management and request log)
---

24. Register a Mock

// Request
POST http://localhost:8000/admin/mocks
{
  "method": "GET",
  "path": "/orders",
  "response": {
    "status": 200,
    "body": { "orders": [] }
  }
}

// Response 201
{
  "id": "e3b0c442-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx",
  "method": "GET",
  "path": "/orders",
  "response": { "status": 200, "body": { "orders": [] } }
}

---
25. List All Mocks

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/admin/mocks

// Response 200
[
  {
    "id": "e3b0c442-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx",
    "method": "GET",
    "path": "/orders",
    "response": { "status": 200, "body": { "orders": [] } }
  }
]

---
26. Delete a Mock by ID

// Request
DELETE http://localhost:8000/admin/mocks/e3b0c442-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

// Response 204
(no body)

---
27. Delete a Mock — Not Found

// Request
DELETE http://localhost:8000/admin/mocks/nonexistent-id

// Response 404
{ "error": "Mock not found" }

---
28. Clear All Mocks

// Request
DELETE http://localhost:8000/admin/mocks

// Response 204
(no body)

---
29. Get Request Log

// Request
GET http://localhost:8000/admin/requests

// Response 200
[
  {
    "method": "POST",
    "path": "/users",
    "headers": { "Content-Type": "application/json", "..." : "..." },
    "body": { "name": "Dave Lee" },
    "timestamp": "2026-04-13T10:30:00.000000+00:00"
  }
]

---
30. Clear Request Log

// Request
DELETE http://localhost:8000/admin/requests

// Response 204
(no body)
